Package: opensand
Architecture: any
Section: metapackages
Depends: libopensand-conf, libopensand-output, libopensand-rt, opensand-core-bin, libopensand-plugin, opensand-daemon
Description: Packages for OpenSAND, a satellite emulation platform.
 This metapackage is to ease the installation of OpenSAND daemon environnment.

